{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roll slimes to solve puzzles on your adventure in an odd little village.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/slime_color_change2.gif?t=1732704150\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roll the blue slime into the goal to unlock the path to the next area.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sometimes, moving stuff around will also move the story along!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight enemies in puzzle battles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore Blue Slime Village, the stage for this puzzle game, where you'll find gimmicks galore!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/slime_dog.gif?t=1732704150\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The controls are simple. Enjoy a variety of puzzle gimmicks just by moving around.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take your time to think with the puzzles. There's no need to rush your actions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can use hints if you run into a puzzle that you just can't figure out.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Listen to the original chiptune soundtrack by HaL_Bits.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2128600/extras/slime_bike.gif?t=1732704150\" />There are a lot more fun things to discover!</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Shep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2128600/b97628ec2970e4beb667e9c1cae913ae55aaeddd.jpg"},{"name":"Hippert","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2128600/2f74dc1da0b99bd5ec8d6e4234c2898f8fb2f654.jpg"},{"name":"Kenchick","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamsta